{
  "stem": "21437.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Or maybe my father suspected-- as he was occasionally-- when he was coming in, he was bringing bits and pieces of jewelry and what were coins.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So-- and there was somebody-- I was the go-between.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was just like a little street, and there was somebody waiting.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that was for to take it in exchange of bits of food and some information.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I knew one thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was the-- that was-- if my father told me that next time he's going to bring something in, it was outside.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was between him and me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he-- he put a lot of emphasis on it-- that nobody else must know it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because those people in that flat, they were starving.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We were all starving.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So we were prepared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were, as adults-- they were prepared to do anything to-- to prolong the life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They didn't think about the quality of life, you know-- just to have something there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So this was apparently-- he felt this was-- or they felt-- I don't think so that they knew when there were bits and pieces of bread or bits and pieces of food coming.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "This was a time when a couple of bites, you know, made the difference between everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So they didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Just whatever-- whatever somebody brought in, whoever was in the flat-- in this flat, not the rest of it, because there was only always little bits and pieces-- we shared it.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And so, as far as I knew, it was myself and my father.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Nobody else knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And so when they ran up, perhaps my-- my-- my father suspected something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But they didn't find anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
